@startuml Client_CRC

title Client — CRC Diagram



class Client {
  == Responsibilities ==
  Open a TCP socket connection to the chat server
  Authenticate the user through LoginHandler
  Register new user accounts through LoginHandler
  Create and start Sender and Receiver threads
  Wrap outbound text in a Message and pass to Sender
  Close the socket on disconnect
  --
  == Collaborators ==
  LoginHandler
  Encrypter
  Sender
  Receiver
  GUI
}

class LoginHandler {
  (collaborator)
}
class Encrypter {
  (collaborator)
}
class Sender {
  (collaborator)
}
class Receiver {
  (collaborator)
}
class GUI {
  (collaborator)
}

Client --> LoginHandler : authenticates / registers via >
Client --> Encrypter    : creates >
Client --> Sender       : creates & starts >
Client --> Receiver     : creates & starts >
Client <.. GUI          : calls connect(), send(), disconnect() >

@enduml
